<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Ansible Notes on rowstu.net</title><link>https://rowstu.net/ansible/</link><description>Recent content in Ansible Notes on rowstu.net</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><atom:link href="https://rowstu.net/ansible/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Ansible Playbooks</title><link>https://rowstu.net/ansible/playbooks/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://rowstu.net/ansible/playbooks/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;An &lt;strong&gt;Ansible Playbook&lt;/strong&gt; is a YAML file that describes automation tasks:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;What to run&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;On which hosts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In what order&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;With what variables&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Playbooks make automation readable, repeatable, and version-controlled.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id="-anatomy-of-a-playbook"&gt;â–¶ï¸ Anatomy of a Playbook&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A playbook consists of:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;---
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;- &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;Description of the play&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;hosts&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;group_or_host&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;become&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;yes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;/no &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# escalate privileges&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;vars&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# local variables&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;var1&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;tasks&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# task list&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;Task description&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;module_name&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;parameter1&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;parameter2&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;handlers&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# optional event handlers&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id="-key-concepts--syntax"&gt;â–¶ï¸ Key Concepts &amp;amp; Syntax&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Inventory&lt;/strong&gt; determines hosts and groups (INI or YAML).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Modules&lt;/strong&gt; are actions: &lt;code&gt;yum&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;apt&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;user&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;copy&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;service&lt;/code&gt;, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tasks&lt;/strong&gt; are the basic building blocks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Handlers&lt;/strong&gt; run when notified (e.g., restart service on config change).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Roles&lt;/strong&gt; encapsulate reusable logic.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id="-good-naming-conventions"&gt;â–¶ï¸ Good Naming Conventions&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-plaintext" data-lang="plaintext"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;playbooks/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; users.yml
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; packages.yml
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; system_update.yml
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;roles/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; common/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; webserver/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
